dct_title_s: Map of the provinces of Canterbury and Otago (New Zealand) to illustrate the papers of Mr. James M'Kerrow, Dr. J. Haast & Dr. Hector
dct_description_sm: Relief shown by hachures. Major glaciers shown in green. Routes of expeditions are shown. Inset map: Islands of New Zealand. From: The Journal of the Royal Geographical Society of London. Vol. 34, (1864), pp. 56-82, 87-111; held in Firestone Library. Call number: G7 .J687 v.34 1864. Geographic coordinate grid was hand drawn after map was published.
dct_publisher_sm: London : published for the Journal of the Royal Geographical Society by John Murray, Albemarle Street, 1864.
